title: Packers vs Aaron Rodgers, SEC, Adam Silver, NFL QBs
itunes:title: Packers vs Aaron Rodgers, SEC, Adam Silver, NFL QBs
description:
Colin talks about the battle between Aaron Rodgers and Packers management, why the SEC can make their own rules, why he agrees with the schedule change by Adam Silver, and which NFL QBs belong in certain cities. Guests include Chris Broussard, Andrew Whitworth, Howie Long, and Jason McIntyre.
